trans-unit.source: Indicates the window style to use for the invoked program when calling the <xref uid="langword_csharp_Shell" name="Shell" href=""></xref> function.
trans-unit.target: 表示要用於叫用程式呼叫時的視窗樣式<xref uid="langword_csharp_Shell" name="Shell" href=""></xref>函式。

trans-unit.source: When you issue `Shell` commands, you can use the following enumeration members in your code in place of the actual values.
trans-unit.target: 當您發出`Shell`命令，您可以使用下列的列舉型別成員在您的程式碼，用來取代實際的值。

trans-unit.source: The `Style` argument takes the `AppWinStyle` enumeration members.
trans-unit.target: `Style`引數會接受`AppWinStyle`列舉成員。

trans-unit.source: Window is hidden and focus is passed to the hidden window.
trans-unit.target: 隱藏視窗，焦點會傳遞到隱藏的視窗。

trans-unit.source: This member is equivalent to the Visual Basic constant <xref uid="langword_csharp_vbHide" name="vbHide" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 這個成員是相當於 Visual Basic 常數<xref uid="langword_csharp_vbHide" name="vbHide" href=""> </xref>。
